          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1906741976" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11654044226034829916">Beautifully written. Heartbreakingly sad. <br/>Potently emotional. Brilliantly executed. Terrifyingly realistic. Happy ending? You decide.<br/><br/>Undeniably one of the best novels out there. <br/><br/>It is absolutely amazing that this is <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/3953740.Rosamund_Lupton' title='Rosamund Lupton' rel='nofollow noopener'>Rosamund Lupton</a>&apos;s first novel. I was so riveted to the pages that I lost three hours of time before coming up for air. I&apos;m looking forward to reading more novels by this undeniably talented writer! Highly recommended!</span>
  <span id="freeText11654044226034829916" style="display:none">Beautifully written. Heartbreakingly sad. <br />Potently emotional. Brilliantly executed. Terrifyingly realistic. Happy ending? You decide.<br /><br />Undeniably one of the best novels out there. <br /><br />It is absolutely amazing that this is <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/3953740.Rosamund_Lupton" title="Rosamund Lupton" rel="nofollow noopener">Rosamund Lupton</a>'s first novel. I was so riveted to the pages that I lost three hours of time before coming up for air. I'm looking forward to reading more novels by this undeniably talented writer! Highly recommended!</span>
  <a data-text-id="11654044226034829916" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
