<li class='cover' id='bookCover_16156329'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16156329-going-home-again"><img alt="Going Home Again" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1357323815l/16156329._SX98_.jpg" />
